{"type":"message","id":"704b2b39","parentId":"0bf47876","timestamp":"2026-02-15T12:43:26.579Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-02-15 14:43 GMT+2] TELEGRAM MENU FIX & NEWS SENTINEL.\n\n1.  **Force Refresh Menu (`src/menu_refresh.py`):**\n    *   Create script using `python-telegram-bot`.\n    *   Use `application.bot.set_my_commands` with `BotCommandScopeDefault`.\n    *   Commands:\n        *   `/dm_start` - \"🚀 Start HFT Trading\"\n        *   `/dm_stop` - \"🛑 STOP Trading\"\n        *   `/dm_status` - \"📊 Fleet Status\"\n        *   `/dm_dashboard` - \"📈 Dashboard\"\n    *   Run script once. Send message to user: \"Commands refreshed...\"\n\n2.  **News Sentinel (`src/sentinel/news_watcher.py`):**\n    *   Create `src/sentinel/` dir.\n    *   Implement `NewsWatcher` class.\n    *   *Sources:* Use `web_search` tool wrapper (simulated for now via `agent_wrapper` logic or direct RSS/HTML parsing if tools allowed).\n    *   *Keywords:* `Update`, `Operation`, `Case`, `Nerf`, `Buff`.\n    *   *Output:* Append to `docs_archive/MARKET_NEWS.md`.\n\n3.  **Protocol Update (Panic Mode):**\n    *   Update `MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`:\n        *   \"Rule: If `NewsWatcher` flags 'Operation/Major Update', reducing BUY limits by 20% for 24h.\"\n\n4.  **Live News Check:**\n    *   Run `NewsWatcher` once.\n    *   Fetch 1 real headline for CS2 or Dota 2.\n\n5.  **Output:**\n    *   Menu Refresh confirmation.\n    *   Actual News Headline found.\n    *   Protocol updated."}],"timestamp":1771159406577}}
